{"type": "article", "id": 2507, "title": "手绘墙纸", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-23T09:19:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1051, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232526Gdxl1vTJLu3VYCUZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>谁说墙纸只能是小碎花？位于伦敦的时尚及室内设计工作室 </span><span>Eley Kishimoto 近日推出了它们第一个手绘墙纸系列。该系列共有 12 种不同的印花，每种都有几种色彩搭配可供选择，图案都取自工作室过去数年经典设计的重新组合。该系列的每一张墙纸都由设计师 </span><span>Mark Eley and Wakako Kishimoto 在它们的工作室里手绘完成，它们希望在这个到处都是机械乏味的电脑印刷墙纸的时代，用手绘回归传统，并让它焕发新生。</span><a href=\"http://www.eleykishimoto.com/shop/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325253yBPKRNncixzAjHg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232525yXA1IjGQPuTDUMEF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232526YPcu4XJfAEUqphMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.321875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}